com.percussion.pso.syndication
Class PSSynFeedCategory

java.lang.Object
  com.percussion.pso.syndication.PSSynFeedCategory

public class PSSynFeedCategory
extends java.lang.Object

For Media RSS: Allows a taxonomy to be set that gives an indication of the type of media content, and its particular contents. It has 2 optional attributes. music/artist/album/song Arts/Movies/Titles/A/Ace_Ventura_Series/Ace_Ventura_ -_Pet_Detective ycantpark mobile scheme is the URI that identifies the categorization scheme. It is an optional attribute. If this attribute is not included, the default scheme is 'http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/category_schema'. label is the human readable label that can be displayed in end user applications. It is an optional attribute.

Author:
natechadwick
